{
  "stem": "8916.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "However, you know I've already told you that we had a brother who was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] younger, next to the oldest one, who was also with us at the time.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was taken on one of those transports.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bezalel.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bezalel.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably Belzec.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I was at home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was in the house, and my parents were in the house when he was dragged out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the Germans played these games where one had to have a special stamp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when one didn't have the stamp, then they would be taken on the transport.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he didn't get the stamp, and so he was taken away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The guards, the Germans, just came in and dragged him out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were petrified.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We said nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No one said a word.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were all home and no one said-- we were just frozen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a-- a very unreal experience.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And somehow from-- at the time, you know, it was so unbelievable that for years and years after that I thought that he-- he might be still alive.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That I would meet him some place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We never did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We never did find out for absolutely certain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just that he never reappeared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we know that those transports were going directly to the death camps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But there's an incident in a movie called where Schindler goes to retrieve his accountant, because he was taken on a transport by mistake.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He didn't have his papers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so Schindler goes to-- to the railroad station where the transport was being formed and finds his accountant and takes him off the train.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, that was the same transport that my brother was on.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
